<HEADLINE> U.S. Gives Aid for Afghan Drought  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON (AP) -- The United States is donating $500,000 for
emergency drought relief in Afghanistan, the State Department said
Friday.
</P>
<P>
