contract from Triple-A Syracuse on Friday. The outfielder hit .297
with seven home runs and 14 RBIs with Syracuse. ... The Blue Jays
also purchased the contract of RHP Darwin Cubillan. To make room,
Toronto optioned SS Chris Woodward and designated LHP Eric
Gunderson for assignment. ... Attendance was 18,268. ... Escobar
was perfect in four of his first five innings. ... Foulke has
pitched 18 scoreless innings in his last 11 outings.
